{"prompt": "Generate a website for a personalized tutoring service. The website should be cozy and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Cozy Tutoring</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #e0f2f7; /* Very light blue */\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 960px;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            padding: 40px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        h1 {\n            color: #0277bd; /* Brand blue */\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #01579b; /* Darker brand blue */\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n        p {\n            line-height: 1.7;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #0288d1; /* Brand blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 25px;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #03a9f4; /* Lighter brand blue on hover */\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n        .services-list {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .services-list li {\n            background-color: #e3f2fd; /* Lightest blue */\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-left: 5px solid #0288d1; /* Brand blue accent */\n        }\n        .contact-info {\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n        .contact-info a {\n            color: #0277bd; /* Brand blue */\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        .contact-info a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        .hero-section {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #03a9f4, #0288d1); /* Gradient with brand blues */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 60px 40px;\n            border-radius: 15px 15px 0 0;\n            margin: -40px -40px 40px -40px;\n            box-shadow: inset 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .hero-section h1 {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"hero-section\">\n            <h1>Personalized Tutoring for Brighter Futures</h1>\n            <p>Unlock your potential with one-on-one support in a warm and encouraging environment.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <h2>Welcome to Cozy Tutoring!</h2>\n        <p>We believe that learning should be a comfortable and confidence-building experience. Our personalized tutoring sessions are designed to meet your unique needs, helping you grasp complex subjects, build essential skills, and achieve your academic goals.</p>\n\n        <h2>What We Offer</h2>\n        <ul class=\"services-list\">\n            <li>Tailored lesson plans based on individual learning styles.</li>\n            <li>Expert guidance in Math, Science, English, and more.</li>\n            <li>Homework help and test preparation strategies.</li>\n            <li>A supportive and patient learning atmosphere.</li>\n            <li>Flexible scheduling to fit your busy life.</li>\n        </ul>\n\n        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>\n        <p>Our tutors are passionate educators dedicated to fostering a love for learning. We create a relaxed setting where students feel empowered to ask questions, explore new ideas, and overcome challenges. Imagine a quiet, cozy corner where learning clicks \u2013 that's the Cozy Tutoring experience!</p>\n\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Schedule Your First Session</a>\n\n        <div class=\"contact-info\">\n            <p>Ready to embark on your learning journey?</p>\n            <p>Email us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@cozytutoring.com\">info@cozytutoring.com</a></p>\n            <p>Call us at: <a href=\"tel:+1234567890\">+1 (234) 567-890</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}